Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meniru lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habis ribut sama Aizawa, sekarang begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli dengan orang sepertinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu bertingkah murung\Ndan banyak mengeluh, padahal dia lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lemah? Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Sensoji tidak tahu\Nkarena dia dari Kelas B.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sering terlalu banyak berpikir\Nsampai terlambat bergerak,
