Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga, aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati! Nanti kalian jatuh!
