Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sampai nanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eraser Head, sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shota itu terlalu peka sama banyak hal,\Nmakanya jadi terlalu banyak berpikir.
