Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti menjadi pengasuh anak atau guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan asal bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku serius, benar-benar serius.
