Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil langkah terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan efisiensi maksimal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan strategi yang rasional!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Strategi pertama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Posisikan diri di atas kepalanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}arahkan jalur serangan ke langit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Strategi kedua!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tendang benjolan yang belum aktif ke atas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ledakkan di ketinggian yang aman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalah terakhirnya adalah\Nperbedaan ukuran tubuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Strategi untuk mengatasinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Strateginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Strateginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kau yang bisa melindungi semua orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa! Kau pasti bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tahu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti tidak akan kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kalah, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kalah, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya datang sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kalah, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan seranganmu sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shirakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raksasa sebesar itu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa dikalahkan sendirian\Noleh seorang pemula.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa dipercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ini kerja tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rekanku terus menyemangatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shirakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior Kayama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana kondisi luka Shirakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi dia masih semangat menyorakiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi seharusnya tidak terlalu parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa lukanya separah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, cepat ke rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, speaker di sana itu milik Shirakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus membawanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?\NBendanya sudah rusak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin. Tadi Shirakumo terus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi maksudmu, dia menyemangatimu lewat\Nspeaker ini sampai saat-saat terakhirnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lewat speaker yang rusak ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebenarnya kau menyemangati dirimu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kondisimu tadi sangat ekstrem.\NHal seperti itu bisa saja terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang "Semangat,"\N"Terus semangat, Shota."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terus disemangati oleh suaranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawa tandunya! Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aizawa, hadapi penjahat yang bahkan gagal\Ndikalahkan oleh pahlawan pro kelas satu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tetap bertahan\Ndan bertarung sampai akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sendirian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbanggalah, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bukan ini yang kau banggakan,\Napa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sensoji, aku benar-benar iri\Ndengan caramu berpikir yang sederhana itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar suara Shirakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar-benar suaranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyemangatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kami bertemu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia selalu mendorongku dari belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan barusan, selalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya makin deras lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aizawa, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuklah ke dalam. Terus-terusan hujan\Nseperti ini tidak baik untuk kesehatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior Kayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hujan ini mewakili suasana hati kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru saat berbuat kesalahan,\Nkita harus tetap tersenyum seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bertiga akan membuat\Nagensi dan mandiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu rencanaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shota mungkin cocok\Nkerja mengurus anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kalau kau benar-benar niat,\Nkurasa kau bisa melakukan apa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, kalau kita bertiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski satu orang gagal,\Ndua yang lain bisa menutupi kekurangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita bertiga,\Nkurasa kita bisa menyelesaikan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkupinjamkan goggles ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus semangat, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kalah, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana Aizawa akhir-akhir ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, seperti biasa,\Nnilainya di atas rata-rata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu dia mendapatkan nilai lulus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia jadi jauh lebih santai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecenderungan itu juga terlihat\Ndi beberapa mata pelajaran akademiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi saat praktik pertempuran,\Ndia sangat tekun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semenjak insiden tahun lalu itu,\Nrasanya dia jadi lebih stabil,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dengan cara yang aneh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, entah kenapa dia jadi terasa berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilihan rencana kariermu adalah\Nmendirikan agensi pribadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langsung mandiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya orang mencari pengalaman dulu\Ndi kantor pahlawan veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membatasi pekerjaan\Nhanya untuk menumpas penjahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begitu, aku hanya butuh\Nmengandalkan kemampuan bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sederhana dan rasional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aizawa, kau lulus dari U.A.\Nhanya untuk menjadi pemburu bayaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau sudah melewati banyak hal,\Ntapi ini demi masa depanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan lebih matang...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pahlawan bawah tanah yang bekerja sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah sosok pahlawan yang ingin kucapai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tumbuh dengan sangat baik...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menangis, Bu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita foto bareng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, suaraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya sudah berhenti, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Urus kucing itu baik-baik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, Eraser mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau lihat keadaan Hotta bersaudara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku ikut sekalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa tahu ada pelanggan di toko\Nyang mau memelihara kucing ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ini pertama kalinya Howler bertemu dia\Nsejak dia keluar dari rumah sakit, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, aku Takobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Howler, katanya aku pernah mengejarmu\Nsambil melempar batu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa orang ini ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasa, dia tidak punya rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi sekarang tinggal\Ndi tenda bareng Kamayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik juga, seperti sedang berkemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi masa kita mau terus-terusan\Ntinggal di tenda seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bangunkan tempatnya, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toko kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berencana membuka kafe\Ndi bekas gudang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat yang luas, supaya orang-orang\Nseperti mereka bisa bebas keluar-masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, mau buka kafe, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Howler...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak kucing ini lucu sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku gendong sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... em...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, bulunya lembut sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mirip sekali dengan kucingku yang dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kucing milikmu, Howler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ini kucing telantar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, biar aku yang pelihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tako, kita kan mau\Nmulai membangun kafe, ingat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pelihara saja di toko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelihara hewan di tempat makan, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa saja, sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibuat jadi kafe kucing yang estetik,\Npasti banyak yang mau datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis-gadis SMA dan semacamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada gadis SMA yang mau mampir\Nke tempat tongkrongan monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?\NKita tidak akan tahu kalau belum dicoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ayo kita bangun!\NKafe impian kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, kita wajib punya rooftop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tak ada rooftop, mau makan di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Premisnya saja sudah aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sih, mau studio kedap suara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kadang aku ingin teriak kencang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sendiri ingin apa, Shota?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fasilitas yang wajib ada di agensi kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menara kucing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, agensi pahlawan\Ndengan peliharaan kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, jadi kita akan\Nmembawa Sushi ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak enak kalau kita terus menitipkannya\Npada Senior Kayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita bertiga, pasti bisa mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurut senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu... ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin... bagus juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tapi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dikerjakan bersama-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita bertiga,\Nkita pasti bisa melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa menolong siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimulai dari seekor kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah... rencana kami suatu hari nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Eraser! Eraser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pura-pura tidak dengar,\Nperhatikan kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat duduk khusus untukmu ada di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sebelah toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau numpang minum kopi,\Nmasuk lewat pintu belakang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau berkeliaran di depan\Nseperti dewa kemiskinan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bisa mengganggu usaha kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, kehadiran pahlawan sepertimu\Nlumayan menguntungkan untuk keamanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang disebut kredibilitas sosial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sering-sering mampir juga\Nbuat lihat kucing ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kucing ini\Nsudah dapat tempat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya kupikir mustahil,\Ntapi ternyata tetap bisa diselesaikan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuacanya cerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa kusadari,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}langit sudah cerah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kafe kucing, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu rencana yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesekali aku akan mampir untuk menengoknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Captain Celebrity sudah menyelesaikan\Nmasalah di negaranya
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan akan kembali ke Amerika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga akan membantu acara perpisahan\Nyang direncanakan untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Pesta Perpisahan".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Captain!
